🚀 Overview

NovaChain AI Verifier is a web-based system that combines:

- Blockchain Technology (Simulated)
- Artificial Intelligence (Simulated)
- Credential Verification System

🌟 Features

- User Registration & Login
- Student Dashboard
- Institution Dashboard
- Employer Dashboard
- Credential Upload
- Blockchain Verification
- AI Fraud Detection

⚙️ Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- LocalStorage (for simulation)

📱 How to Run

1. Download or clone this repository
2. Open "index.html" in your browser (even on phone)
3. Start using the system

